<P>The Unrea&s;onablene&s;s and Danger of a Peoples renouncing their &s;ubjection to God.</P>
<P>A Sermon, Preached at the General Court of Election, at Hartford in the Colony of Connecticut on May the Tenth 1711.</P>
<P>By <HI>Stephen Buckingham</HI> M. A and Pa&s;tor of the Church in <HI>Norwalk,</HI></P>
